description:
Versatility is the name of the game for the Explorer pants. With their understated styling, technical materials and construction, these pants will take kids from the classroom to the trails. Their lightweight stretchy material has been treated to repel water and resist dirt, keeping kids looking cleaner longer.Midweight nylon blend dries quickly and has just enough spandex for a comfortable stretch.DWR finish helps keep these pants cleaner longer.UPF 50 blocks UV during long days under the sun.Integrated webbing belt helps you cinch in the perfect fit on growing bodies.Zippered hand pockets keep small treasures save.Gusseted crotch means these pants can keep up with active kids.Regular fit.

